(222, 'Resolution 8 (Cg-18)', 'Resolution 08 (Cg-18)', 'https://library.wmo.int/doc_num.php?explnum_id=9827/#page=53', 53, 'Research Board ', '', '2019', 'Cg', '18', 'Resolution', '', 'LTG5-Governance', 'SO5.1-Structures', 'Research Board', '', '', 'SI - Science and Innovation Department', '', 'The Research Board was established and its members were appointed in accordance with Resolution 3 (EC-71). Rules of Procedures developed and submitted to EC-72.', 'Keep in force'),
