(279, 'Resolution 65 (Cg-18)', 'Resolution 65 (Cg-18)', 'https://library.wmo.int/doc_num.php?explnum_id=9827/#page=221', 221, 'WMO and the ocean ', '', '2019', 'Cg', '18', 'Resolution', '', 'LTG5-Governance', 'Policy requiring coordination', 'Ocean', '', 'Ocean', 'O - Cross-cutting Coordinator for Ocean', '', 'WMO has provided input to the UN Ocean Decade preparatory process throughout 2020 and will continue contributions - noting that the Decade officially commenced in January 2021. Part of this contribution has included the JCB drafting the WMO-IOC Strategy. A WMO Ocean Plan will be reported in 2022 - delayed due to COVID.', 'Keep in force'),
