(281, 'Resolution 67 (Cg-18)', 'Resolution 67 (Cg-18)', 'https://library.wmo.int/doc_num.php?explnum_id=9827/#page=227', 227, 'WMO scientific and technological support to the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change and climate policy ', '', '2019', 'Cg', '18', 'Resolution', '', 'LTG3-Research', 'SO3.3-Science for policy', 'Climate policy', '', 'Climate', 'IPCC - Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change', '', 'The ad-hoc Task Force established through the Resolution has drafted recommendations concerning the implementation of CMIP and CORDEX delivery to IPCC, which are being incorporated into recommendations to the Executive Council addressing the related organizational and financial aspects.', 'Keep in force'),
