(283, 'Resolution 69 (Cg-18)', 'Resolution 69 (Cg-18)', 'https://library.wmo.int/doc_num.php?explnum_id=9827/#page=232', 232, 'Guidelines on the Role and Operations of WMO Regional and Representative Offices ', '', '2019', 'Cg', '18', 'Resolution', '', 'LTG5-Governance', 'SO5.1-Structures', 'Regional associations', '', '', 'MS - Member Services and Development Department', '', 'Volume II of Guidelines on Operations of WMO regional and Representative Offices is currently under development (to be finalized by end of 2020). It covers the internal management of the Regional and Representative Offices and is intended to serve as a manual for all WMO staff members serving in the field and at WMO headquarters. It provides guidance on all aspects of operations – setting up an office, protocol, monitoring and reporting, financial management, procurement, HR matters, among others.', 'Keep in force'),
